and build-related files are licensed under a different, generally more open
license.

In general, you can consider this project to be licensed as LGPL 2.1 or later,
or LGPL 2.1 or later and BSD 3-clause.

The documentation of this project is licensed under the Public Documentation
License version 1.0.

See source headers for the specific license(s) of a file.

Texts of applicable licenses can be found in the LICENSES/ directory of
the repository at <https://github.com/FirebirdSQL/jaybird>.

